# Example "Good First Issue" Ideas for Your Repository:

## Documentation Improvements
- Add screenshots to FSM dashboard documentation
- Create troubleshooting guide for common network issues
- Write deployment guide for specific cloud providers
- Translate README sections to other languages

## Easy Code Contributions  
- Add new health check validations
- Create additional configuration templates
- Implement new scenario types
- Add support for additional security tools

## Community Enhancements
- Create beginner-friendly video tutorials
- Design project logos and visual assets
- Write blog posts about deployment experiences
- Create social media content for project promotion

